title: mondaysRmurder EP 5: Where is Michaela Garecht?
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: UPDATE: On December 22nd, 2020, police arrested David Misch, 59, for the alleged abduction and murder of Michaela Garecht. According to police, Mischs' fingerprints match the fingerprints found of Michaelas' scooter left outside the Rainbow Market. Witnesses also placed Misch in Hayward, California, near the Rainbow Market, on the day Michaela was abducted. Misch will be arraigned Tuesday, December 29th. I will make another video giving you an update on this case.
